{
  "stem": "1873.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were afraid of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But we find out that this was another group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we get together, so there was about 80 people together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Now, a tragedy involved, which is not nice to talk about that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But we can't talk only about nice things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "If my story should be a document, I must tell you everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Very bad things happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We did run for about three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "In the daytime, we were sitting quietly, because planes were circling over the forest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And  in two days, and it was when we were running, Sasha instructed us, we should run.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We should go one after another one, because he left-- before, we were running in groups.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "This place was devastated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And so, at one point, I remember a night, and we were going out, from the forest, through a meadow, to another forest.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I turned my head, and I have seen this snake of people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I understood, no, it's impossible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We will be caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But anyway, after a while, there was a meadow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "We relaxed there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And Sasha said, now, we will go and find out where we are.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "We heard a train passing by, not far away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And he did asked one of us to collect money, because we had money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Only the ones which is the banned organization picked up money from the storeroom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And we did give him money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "He said, this is for food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And he picked up 10 people, all the guns, all the people who had  the guns-- 10 people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And we didn't let him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We had a feeling, something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "We said, one person with a gun must stay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Give us Szlomo Szmajzner from Pulawy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And he didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Even that, he wanted to take away the gun from him.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
